summary: Praveen from ITC assisted Jitendra Kumar in filing a complaint regarding a defective WhatsApp-branded product he purchased. Despite raising the issue, the product continued to be sold to customers. To resolve the issue, Praveen arranged for an executive to visit Kumar's address to collect the faulty product and provide a fresh one. They also discussed the need for proper quality control measures. The conversation was interrupted several times due to network issues. Both parties agreed to wait for a call back from the respective teams. The call ended with the assurance that Kumar would be contacted regarding the replacement.

The customer support explained that they would send an executive to collect the product and provide a fresh one. The customer was then asked to share a photo of the product but the customer support couldn't receive it due to network issues. The support assured the customer that they would call them back directly with the visit details of the executive, and they thanked the customer for calling ITC. The customer then repeated their number, and the support confirmed it as 6280-730-418, and then ended the call.
